<li id="cite_note-griswold-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-griswold_7-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFGriswold2003">Griswold, Charles (2003-12-22). <a href="http://plato.stanford.edu/archives/spr2004/entries/plato-rhetoric/" class="external text" title="http://plato.stanford.edu/archives/spr2004/entries/plato-rhetoric/" rel="nofollow">"Plato on Rhetoric and Poetry"</a>. in Edward N. Zalta. <i>The Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy</i> (Spring 2004 Edition ed.). Stanford, CA: The Metaphysics Research Lab, Center for the Study of Language and Information, <a href="/wiki/Stanford_University" title="Stanford University">Stanford University</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://plato.stanford.edu/archives/spr2004/entries/plato-rhetoric/" class="external free" title="http://plato.stanford.edu/archives/spr2004/entries/plato-rhetoric/" rel="nofollow">http://plato.stanford.edu/archives/spr2004/entries/plato-rhetoric/</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-06-08</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Plato+on+Rhetoric+and+Poetry&amp;rft.atitle=The+Stanford+Encyclopedia+of+Philosophy&amp;rft.aulast=Griswold&amp;rft.aufirst=Charles&amp;rft.au=Griswold%2C+Charles&amp;rft.date=2003-12-22&amp;rft.edition=Spring+2004+Edition&amp;rft.place=Stanford%2C+CA&amp;rft.pub=The+Metaphysics+Research+Lab%2C+Center+for+the+Study+of+Language+and+Information%2C+%5B%5BStanford+University%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fplato.stanford.edu%2Farchives%2Fspr2004%2Fentries%2Fplato-rhetoric%2F&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Aestheticization_of_violence"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
