<li id="cite_note-alsford-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-alsford_9-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFAlsford2004">Alsford, Stephen (2004-02-29). <a href="http://www.trytel.com/~tristan/towns/florilegium/lcdth_i.html" class="external text" title="http://www.trytel.com/~tristan/towns/florilegium/lcdth_i.html" rel="nofollow">"Death - Introductory essay"</a>. <i>Florilegium Urbanum</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.trytel.com/~tristan/towns/florilegium/lcdth_i.html" class="external free" title="http://www.trytel.com/~tristan/towns/florilegium/lcdth_i.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.trytel.com/~tristan/towns/florilegium/lcdth_i.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-06-08</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Death+-+Introductory+essay&amp;rft.atitle=Florilegium+Urbanum&amp;rft.aulast=Alsford&amp;rft.aufirst=Stephen&amp;rft.au=Alsford%2C+Stephen&amp;rft.date=2004-02-29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.trytel.com%2F%7Etristan%2Ftowns%2Fflorilegium%2Flcdth_i.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Aestheticization_of_violence"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
